<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0017', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:196'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='196:211'>　易學辨惑　　　　　　易類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='211:217'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='217:243'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案易學辨惑一卷宋邵伯温撰伯温</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='243:266'>　　　　字子文邵子之子也南渡後官至利路轉運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='266:289'>　　　　副使事蹟具宋史儒林傳按沈括夢溪筆談</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='289:312'>　　　　載江南鄭夬字揚庭曽為一書談易後見兵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='312:335'>　　　　部員外郎秦玠論夬所談玠駭然曰何處得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='335:361'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0017', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='361:384'>　　　　此法嘗遇一異人授此歴數推徃古興衰運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='384:407'>　　　　歴無不皆騐西都邵雍亦知大畧云云盖當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='407:430'>　　　　時以邵子能前知故引之以重其術伯温謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='430:453'>　　　　邵子易受之李之才之才受之穆修修受之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='453:476'>　　　　陳摶平時未嘗妄以語人惟大名王天悦滎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='476:499'>　　　　陽張子望嘗從學又皆蚤死秦玠鄭夬嘗欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='499:522'>　　　　從學皆不之許天悦感疾且卒夬賂其僕於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='522:545'>　　　　卧内竊得之遂以為學著易傳易測明範五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='545:571'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0017', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='571:594'>　　　　經明用數書皆破碎妄作穿鑿不根因撰此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='594:617'>　　　　書以辨之宋史邵子本傳頗採其説考書錄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='617:640'>　　　　解題有鄭夬易傳十三卷宋史藝文志有鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='640:663'>　　　　夬時用書二十卷明用書九卷易傳詞三卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='663:686'>　　　　易傳詞後語一卷今並佚司馬光集有進鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='686:709'>　　　　夬易測劄子稱其不泥隂陽不涉怪妄専用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='709:732'>　　　　人事指明六爻求之等倫誠難多得與伯温</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='732:755'>　　　　所辨褒貶迥殊光亦知易之人不應背馳如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='755:781'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0017', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='781:804'>　　　　是以理推之夬竊邵子之書而變化其説以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='804:827'>　　　　隂求駕乎其上所撰易測必尚随爻演義不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='827:850'>　　　　涉術數故光有不泥隂陽不涉怪妄之薦至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='850:873'>　　　　其時用書之類則純言占卜之法故伯温辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='873:896'>　　　　而闢之其兼易測言之者不過憎及儲胥之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='896:919'>　　　　意耳朱彛尊經義考載此書註曰未見此本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='919:942'>　　　　自永樂大典錄出盖明初猶存宋史藝文志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='942:965'>　　　　但題辨惑一卷無易學字永樂大典則有之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='965:991'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0017', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='991:1014'>　　　　與書錄解題相合故今仍以易學辨惑著錄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1014:1032'>　　　　焉乾隆四十六年九月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1032:1064'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1064:1088'>　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸　費　墀</span><br/>
